text: "Don't Change" is a 1982 song by Australian new wave band INXS and taken from their third studio album Shabooh Shoobah. It is their first international single. It went to number 14 in Australia and number 80 in the United States. ==Track listing== 7" single Track listing == References == Category:1982 songs Category:INXS songs Category:Bruce Springsteen songs Category:Limp Bizkit songs
